headline: Insights Into Phillips 66 (PSX) Q2: Wall Street Projections for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for Phillips 66 (PSX), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended June 2025.
